263
00:19:09,193 --> 00:19:11,779
Walau muda, dia pintar membaca pasar

264
00:19:11,862 --> 00:19:13,322
dan hebat membuat keputusan.

265
00:19:13,406 --> 00:19:15,700
Dia pintar baca pasar
dan hebat membuat keputusan?

266
00:19:16,742 --> 00:19:17,868
Menarik.

267
00:19:19,161 --> 00:19:20,162
Apa?

268
00:19:20,329 --> 00:19:21,914
Aku melihatmu seperti itu.

269
00:19:26,293 --> 00:19:27,253
Terima kasih.

270
00:19:29,004 --> 00:19:30,506
Kalau begitu menurutmu,

271
00:19:31,257 --> 00:19:33,592
bagaimana Park Saeroyi?

272
00:19:44,395 --> 00:19:46,188
Apa yang kulihat dari Park Saeroyi

273
00:19:48,399 --> 00:19:49,984
