427
00:30:27,546 --> 00:30:29,506
Kau bukan pembual, 'kan?

428
00:30:31,133 --> 00:30:32,134
Pembual?

429
00:30:33,051 --> 00:30:34,219
Apa maksudmu?

430
00:30:37,848 --> 00:30:39,141
