453
00:32:39,928 --> 00:32:41,596
Kau ingin kerja paruh waktu di sini?

454
00:32:42,264 --> 00:32:43,640
Ya, Bos.

455
00:32:46,017 --> 00:32:47,769
Karena aku penggemar Jo Yi-seo.

456
00:32:50,230 --> 00:32:51,398
Kau gagal.

457
00:32:52,148 --> 00:32:53,400
Gagal.

458
00:32:53,483 --> 00:32:55,443
Tak ada orang yang bisa dipilih.

459
00:33:12,002 --> 00:33:14,796
Aku datang karena lowongan pekerjaan.

460
00:33:14,879 --> 00:33:17,549
- Apa kalian masih mencari pekerja?
- Kau diterima.

461
00:33:18,550 --> 00:33:19,676
- Apa?
- Apa?

462
00:33:19,759 --> 00:33:20,677
Maksudku...

463
00:33:21,052 --> 00:33:23,263
Ya, kau diterima.

464
00:33:23,346 --> 00:33:24,806
Tidak, kami masih mencari. Bos!

465
00:33:26,308 --> 00:33:27,684
Wawancara selesai.

466
00:33:29,894 --> 00:33:30,854
Kau...

467
